# Scripts

| Script | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `release.py` | Build dist, validate, audits (run before release) |
| `audit_quality.py` | Run all quality audits (summary) |
| `merge_plant_data.py` | Build dist/ from source |
| `validate_json.py` | Schema & structure validation |
| `schema.py` | Shared constants (CATEGORY_ORDER, enums) |
| `sort_plants.py` | Sort by category, then id |
| `extract_by_category.py` | Extract by category for audit sessions |
| `improve_plant_data.py` | Infer missing soilPhPreference, drainagePreference, plantLifeSpan (`--dry-run` first) |
| `reorganize_plants.py` | Apply REMOVE_IDS, CATEGORY_CHANGES (edit in file first) |
| `audit_metadata_completeness.py` | Line-by-line metadata audit |
| `audit_scientific_names.py` | Check commonExamples for accepted names |
| `audit_duplicates.py` | Duplicate typeNames (same name across entries), genus/species overlap, similar typeNames |
| `audit_generic_descriptions.py` | Flag generic descriptions |
| `audit_translation_sync.py` | Verify EN/ES/ZH coverage |
| `audit_target_language.py` | CJK in EN/ES, English in ZH commonExamples, English phrases in ZH/ES |
| `audit_also_known_as.py` | Scientific names, subtypes, duplicate typeName in AKA (with `--fix`) |
| `audit_toxicity_care_tips.py` | Toxicity metadata vs care tips alignment |
| `ensure_complementary_aka.py` | Add complementary aka when missing: nickname typeName→formal; formal typeName→nickname. Aka is optional; remove if redundant (audit). |
| `audit_toxicity_unknown.py` | List plants with unknown toxicity by category |
| `translate_typenames.py` | Translate EN typeNames → ZH or ES (`--lang zh-Hans` / `--lang es`) |
| `add_common_alias_to_description.py` | Add formal names/aliases from commonExamples to description (use `--dry-run` first) |
| `optimize_duplicate_typenames.py` | Differentiate duplicate typeNames (same name across entries). Use `--dry-run` first, then `--fix` |
